{"tid":2165481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"門診免費驗毒拍烏蠅，逾萬人無交樽，全民檢測料僅一成人參與","createTime":"2020-08-20T00:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T16:51:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":469,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"ff182b902f9d000265d872ce08e8ef68f89732c1","tid":2165481,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:36:42.000Z","msg":"本港第三波武肺疫情近日明顯放緩，林鄭政府才強推全民病毒檢測，更揚言會有500萬人參與。本報分析醫管局普通科門診派樽計劃數據，發現自7月27日計劃開展至8月15日，派發率只有85.4%，收回率更只有約67.7%，有門診一日僅得30多名市民索取樣本包，場面冷清，反映公眾參與檢測意欲低。有專家直指，只有自覺有感染風險及有病徵者，才有動機參與檢測，料全民檢測最多只有50萬人參與，僅及政府估算的一成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/AAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FAAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRuff3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=a8996329\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FAAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI%2F&h=365bd58e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/AAAVEFW7RREMJD2OEKAHNPPBHI/</a>"},{"pid":"357530881380a652a266518d69683c38186e3d49","tid":2165481,"uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":173,"score":-158,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"任職裝修的淇仔指公司有同事確診，所以取樽檢測，認為疫情仍嚴重，就算驗過一次，日後的全民檢測也會參與，以免染疫累及家人。"},{"pid":"e857157b141023e59b2a5d0e43b46147b6b580c8","tid":2165481,"uid":42188,"like":262,"dislike":0,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:08:18.000Z","msg":"支那：油水已get<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b865a9602d3ac793c8937a208acb664b857f9638","tid":2165481,"uid":26770,"like":239,"dislike":0,"score":239,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"沉默的藍絲呢"},{"pid":"8529a664cfb886cd4fa2c3a78f5a7158f039f904","tid":2165481,"uid":59142,"like":135,"dislike":1,"score":134,"quote":{"pid":"b865a9602d3ac793c8937a208acb664b857f9638","tid":2165481,"uid":26770,"like":239,"dislike":0,"score":239,"citedBy":5,"replyTime"